115→													viewBox="0 0 24 24"
116→												>
117→													<path d="M17 2V13M22 11V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7.236a2 2 0 00-1.789 1.106l-3.5 7A2 2 0 003.736 13H8v6a3 3 0 003 3v0a3 3 0 003-3v-6h3a2 2 0 002-2z" />
118→												</svg>
